  <wpt lat="44.878202984109521" lon="20.355767011642456">
    <ele>100.9688</ele>
    <time>2014-04-08T17:24:29Z</time>
    <name>01 Dunav Camping Donau Beograd</name>
    <cmt>Beograd Camping Donau
Price: 2 x 8,-€/night/person
Campground: next to the Donau river, clean, quiet 
Sanitair: clean (we were the only guests), OK
Electricity: availabe
Wifi: no
Price is OK for a quite night (about 7-10Km away from the highway) and with a hot shower. 
</cmt>
    <desc>Beograd Camping Donau
Price: 2 x 8,-€/night/person
Campground: next to the Donau river, clean, quiet 
Sanitair: clean (we were the only guests), OK
Electricity: availabe
Wifi: no
Price is OK for a quite night (about 7-10Km away from the highway) and with a hot shower. 
</desc>
