    <time>2014-04-10T03:39:55Z</time>
    <name>02 BC Edrine hills</name>
    <cmt>First (wild) camp in Turkey not far from the border. Off the highway in the fields in the middle of nowhere. Quite night exept for some far away factory noise in the early morning. 
