  <wpt lat="32.640597028657794" lon="51.715303966775537">
    <ele>1587.8889999999999</ele>
    <time>2014-04-15T07:45:52Z</time>
    <name>08 BC Gabhir Garden Isfahan</name>
    <cmt>Used by many overlanders. Parking with fence and police surveillance and public toilets. Small growcery stores accross the street which supply bread, water, an others... Initialy the police did not want us to sleep here. After some discussion we were allowed to park and sleep in front of the police caravan on the parking. 
</cmt>
    <desc>Used by many overlanders. Parking with fence and police surveillance and public toilets. Small growcery stores accross the street which supply bread, water, an others... Initialy the police did not want us to sleep here. After some discussion we were allowed to park and sleep in front of the police caravan on the parking. 
</desc>
    <sym>Campground</sym>
    <type>user</type>
    <extensions>
      <gpxx:WaypointExtension>
        <gpxx:DisplayMode>SymbolAndName</gpxx:DisplayMode>
      </gpxx:WaypointExtension>
