    <ele>179.72640000000001</ele>
    <time>2014-04-23T02:31:57Z</time>
    <name>15 BC close to highway to Bukhara</name>
    <cmt>Wild camp off the new highway to Bukhara within the dunes. First we tried the other site of the highway direct at the river. However, military visited us and we needed to leave as the border with Turkmenitan is too close. 
