  <wpt lat="39.77391698397696" lon="64.419183963909745">
    <ele>280.72120000000001</ele>
    <time>2014-04-23T11:49:47Z</time>
    <name>16 BC parking hotel Asia Bukhara</name>
    <cmt>Wild camp on the parking of the hotel Asia Bukhara protected by fence and security guard. Clean toilets, water and wifi available. Asked hotel manager if we could stay. Payed parking guard 2000 Sum (~0,65 Euro). Excellent location direct in front of the old town. 

</cmt>
    <desc>Wild camp on the parking of the hotel Asia Bukhara protected by fence and security guard. Clean toilets, water and wifi available. Asked hotel manager if we could stay. Payed parking guard 2000 Sum (~0,65 Euro). Excellent location direct in front of the old town. 

</desc>
