  <wpt lat="39.656323911622167" lon="66.979286670684814">
    <ele>0.02</ele>
    <time>1970-01-01T00:00:00Z</time>
    <name>17 BC guesthouse Bahodir Samarquand</name>
    <cmt>This great place is well known among Uzbekistan budget travelers. You meet here interesting people from all over the world. Also the location can not be better as everything is in walking distance just behind the Registan. We paid for using shower breakfast/dinner and therefore we could sleep in our cars in front of the guesthouse. The guesthouse did do the mandatory registration for us. 
</cmt>
