  <wpt lat="37.48670700006187" lon="71.56212299130857">
    <ele>2146.049</ele>
    <time>2014-04-30T11:02:55Z</time>
    <name>22 BC guesthouse Pamir Lodge Kohrog</name>
    <cmt>Pamir Lodge. This is the place where you meet other overlanders and travellers. The garden is a pleasant spot overlooked by a wide open balcony where travellers enjoy their cooking or exhanging experiances. The lodge was established to fund the local jamoat khana. 
Price: 2 x 6,-U$/night/person
Campground: clean, quiet, we did sleep in our car 
Sanitair: OK, shower with warm water and toilet
Electricity: available
Wifi: yes (free)

</cmt>
