  <wpt lat="37.037691967561841" lon="72.656940026208758">
    <ele>2815.2020000000002</ele>
    <time>2014-05-03T10:17:28Z</time>
    <name>24 BC homestay</name>
    <cmt>Guesthouse in on the Wakhan valley road. We did take this place as we wanted to stay protected (after a fense, wall) 
Price: 5 U$/night/car, the owner wanted first from us 15 U$ (for what?) which we refused to pay
Campground: after fense
Sanitair: not existing, toilet with hole in the ground 
Electricity: no
Wifi: no
