  <wpt lat="38.182104974985123" lon="73.986670039594173">
    <ele>3615.9409999999998</ele>
    <time>2014-05-04T09:46:48Z</time>
    <name>25 BC guesthouse Murgab</name>
    <cmt>Normally the guesthouse opens first in June. We could stay as we don't needed a room. Showers were not working jet. Toilet was OK. It was nice we could cook and eat in the veranda as we had cold wether with showers in the evening. The veranda is warm as long as the sun shines. Beginning of May it gets cold after sunset and we had around freezing temperetaure during the night. 
Price: 5 U$/night/car
Campground: 2 cars can take place after the fense next to the house. We did sleep in our car
Sanitair: we didn't use the shower as the guesthouse was still closed, European style toilet was OK
Electricity: yes (we didn't use)
Wifi: no
</cmt>
    <desc>Normally the guesthouse opens first in June. We could stay as we don't needed a room. Showers were not working jet. Toilet was OK. It was nice we could cook and eat in the veranda as we had cold wether with showers in the evening. The veranda is warm as long as the sun shines. Beginning of May it gets cold after sunset and we had around freezing temperetaure during the night. 
