    <ele>2111.3240000000001</ele>
    <time>2014-05-13T02:47:27Z</time>
    <name>29 BC Ala Archa NP</name>
    <cmt>Wild camp within the Ala Archa National Park. On the site of the road (parking lot). Not so quite during weekends and summer season. It was freezing during the night given the high altitutde and early season. Ideal start hiking trips from here. 




