  <wpt lat="41.429136749356985" lon="76.021566716954112">
    <ele>0</ele>
    <time>1970-01-01T00:00:00Z</time>
    <name>31 BC the Celestial mountains Naryn</name>
    <cmt>The Celestial mountains Naryn. A good and convenient place to relax a few days and to get everything washed and cleaned. They have shared toilets and hot showers in rather small compartments which are cleaned every day. They serve a better than expected breakfast and dinner at the basement dining room. All in all a good all rounder and good value but lacked the character of the other homestay places we stayed in. 
Price: 200 Sum (2,60€) /person/night (use of hot shower inlcuded), 200 Sum (2,60 €) /person for breakfast, 350 Sum (4,55€)/person for a good dinner 
Campground: after fence/wall, we did sleep in our car, up to 5-6 cars can park next to the guesthouse
Sanitair: European style toilet, hot shower (old but clean) 
Laundery service: 300 Sumoni (3,90€/machine)
Electricity: we didn't use
Wifi: yes (free)

</cmt>
    <desc>The Celestial mountains Naryn. A good and convenient place to relax a few days and to get everything washed and cleaned. They have shared toilets and hot showers in rather small compartments which are cleaned every day. They serve a better than expected breakfast and dinner at the basement dining room. All in all a good all rounder and good value but lacked the character of the other homestay places we stayed in. 
Price: 200 Sum (2,60€) /person/night (use of hot shower inlcuded), 200 Sum (2,60 €) /person for breakfast, 350 Sum (4,55€)/person for a good dinner 
Campground: after fence/wall, we did sleep in our car, up to 5-6 cars can park next to the guesthouse
