  <wpt lat="41.794116999953985" lon="77.036236999556422">
    <ele>2931.297</ele>
    <time>2014-05-18T10:31:28Z</time>
    <name>32 BC return (snow and broken bridge)</name>
    <cmt>Our plan was to pass the mountains to get to Lake Issyk Kul. This route is really remote and not often used due to snow conditions. We needed to return as both snow and a broken bridge made it impossible to continue. However we were very happy to have experienced this fantastic scenery. 
</cmt>
    <desc>Our plan was to pass the mountains to get to Lake Issyk Kul. This route is really remote and not often used due to snow conditions. We needed to return as both snow and a broken bridge made it impossible to continue. However we were very happy to have experienced this fantastic scenery. 
</desc>
    <sym>Campground</sym>
    <type>user</type>
    <extensions>
      <gpxx:WaypointExtension>
        <gpxx:DisplayMode>SymbolAndName</gpxx:DisplayMode>
      </gpxx:WaypointExtension>
