    <ele>0.02</ele>
    <time>1970-01-01T00:00:00Z</time>
    <name>34 BC Shonzy Parking Hotel</name>
    <cmt>We stayed next to the hotel behind the fence. Very dirty toilets and we did not take a shower given the status of the toilet. Not recommendable. Cost 5U$/person. 

