  <wpt lat="43.922749925404787" lon="78.790233135223389">
    <ele>0.02</ele>
    <time>1970-01-01T00:00:00Z</time>
    <name>35 BC at the Altyn Emel NP</name>
    <cmt>Wild camp at one of the ranger station of the Altyn Emil National Park. What an unforgettable place! We had the honor to sleep one cozy night under the protective arms of Eva. Eva is a 700 years old giant tree. Evas “arms” are so unbelievably long – we never saw something like that. 100% recommendable. 
</cmt>
    <desc>Wild camp at one of the ranger station of the Altyn Emil National Park. What an unforgettable place! We had the honor to sleep one cozy night under the protective arms of Eva. Eva is a 700 years old giant tree. Evas “arms” are so unbelievably long – we never saw something like that. 100% recommendable. 
</desc>
    <sym>Campground</sym>
    <type>user</type>
    <extensions>
      <gpxx:WaypointExtension>
