  <wpt lat="43.22627772577107" lon="76.919222194701433">
    <ele>976.09690000000001</ele>
    <time>1970-01-01T00:00:00Z</time>
    <name>36 BC Almaty at University parking</name>
    <cmt>Wild camp on the guarded parking lot of the Almaty University. This is a good wild camp within the city. We arrived in the evening (empty parking) and asked the guard if we could park and stay for the night. The first answer was no. Be our guests was their second answer when we informed him that we are Germans travelling the world. 

</cmt>
    <desc>Wild camp on the guarded parking lot of the Almaty University. This is a good wild camp within the city. We arrived in the evening (empty parking) and asked the guard if we could park and stay for the night. The first answer was no. Be our guests was their second answer when we informed him that we are Germans travelling the world. 

</desc>
    <sym>Campground</sym>
