  <wpt lat="52.547848485410213" lon="85.196013450622559">
    <ele>0.02</ele>
    <time>1970-01-01T00:00:00Z</time>
    <name>39 BC on hotel Parking Biysk</name>
    <cmt>Recommendable place with good restaurant (dinner 606Rubel, 12,10 Euro for 2 people). 24 hour video surveilance + parking guard. Parking mainly used by truckdrivers, so noisy. Hotel toilets can be used and are very clean. 
</cmt>
