  <wpt lat="48.963906113058329" lon="89.96553897857666">
    <ele>0.02</ele>
    <time>1970-01-01T00:00:00Z</time>
    <name>41 BC Blue Wolf guesthouse Olgi</name>
    <cmt>Not recommendable. Promissed hot shower which was not available both in the evening and morning. Breakfast was included and promised for 8 O'clock but not served. In the morning additional payment was requested. This place is for back pakers sleeping in the Ger's but not for cars as only 1 car can park. We could put however our car behind the fence which is exceptional since there were no tourists jet. 
Price: 10,-U$/night/car
Campground: nor really quite due to trafic and dogs, we did sleep in our cars 
Sanitair: shower and toilet
Electricity: yes
Wifi: yes (included in price)


</cmt>
    <desc>Not recommendable. Promissed hot shower which was not available both in the evening and morning. Breakfast was included and promised for 8 O'clock but not served. In the morning additional payment was requested. This place is for back pakers sleeping in the Ger's but not for cars as only 1 car can park. We could put however our car behind the fence which is exceptional since there were no tourists jet. 
Price: 10,-U$/night/car
Campground: nor really quite due to trafic and dogs, we did sleep in our cars 
Sanitair: shower and toilet
