  <wpt lat="45.018532890826464" lon="101.08290910720825">
    <ele>0.02</ele>
    <time>1970-01-01T00:00:00Z</time>
    <name>46 BC no route to Bayanlig?</name>
    <cmt>WC attempt to reach Bayanlig. However the GPS track data was misleading us. We believe that the data was added afterwards and not in sync with the real situation. We initially wanted to reach the Gobi via Bayanlig. We finally decided to wild camp in this quite location in the middle of nowhere and continue the next day in the direction of Dalanzagad. 

</cmt>
    <desc>WC attempt to reach Bayanlig. However the GPS track data was misleading us. We believe that the data was added afterwards and not in sync with the real situation. We initially wanted to reach the Gobi via Bayanlig. We finally decided to wild camp in this quite location in the middle of nowhere and continue the next day in the direction of Dalanzagad. 

</desc>
    <sym>Campground</sym>
    <type>user</type>
