    <ele>1465.452</ele>
    <time>2014-06-18T10:17:49Z</time>
    <name>55 BC Kharakorum</name>
    <cmt>Stayed 2 nights within the camp. We did not use the sanitair facilities. We had dinner for 7.500 Tenge/P (3,- Euro), a beer 3.500 Tenge/P and breakfast 6.500 Tenge/P. We did not need to pay for the camping. Quite campground. 
</cmt>
