  <wpt lat="47.478349981829524" lon="101.45790003240108">
    <ele>1679.6410000000001</ele>
    <time>2014-06-21T01:43:01Z</time>
    <name>56 BC Fairfields Tsetserleg</name>
    <cmt>Fair fields is a great guesthouse, bakery and café! The café has a really good menu for breakfast, lunch and dinner. Try the giant whopper bugger. The pastry is great as it comes from the own bakery. The whole guesthouse is very clean and well managed. Wifi is once 1.000 Tenge (0,25 Euro). We stayed in front of the guesthouse in our car (free). A nice hot shower is 3.000 Tenge (1,10 Euro). The owner of Fair fields is happy to provide you with his GPS tracks and useful tips for example towards lake Khovskol.</cmt>
    <desc>Fair fields is a great guesthouse, bakery and café! The café has a really good menu for breakfast, lunch and dinner. Try the giant whopper bugger. The pastry is great as it comes from the own bakery. The whole guesthouse is very clean and well managed. Wifi is once 1.000 Tenge (0,25 Euro). We stayed in front of the guesthouse in our car (free). A nice hot shower is 3.000 Tenge (1,10 Euro). The owner of Fair fields is happy to provide you with his GPS tracks and useful tips for example towards lake Khovskol.</desc>
    <sym>Campground</sym>
    <type>user</type>
    <extensions>
      <gpxx:WaypointExtension>
