  <wpt lat="49.476199988275766" lon="105.09119999594986">
    <ele>1026.809</ele>
    <time>2014-06-28T03:03:12Z</time>
    <name>63 BC Amarbayasgalant monastry</name>
    <cmt>About 100 families from Ulaanbataar visit the Amarbayasgalant monastery and camp here over the weekend. So the monastery ceremony is very crowded on Saturdays by the locals. We were the only tourists attending the ceremony. The fotos were taken on Sunday when everybody was on their way back to UB. 
</cmt>
    <desc>About 100 families from Ulaanbataar visit the Amarbayasgalant monastery and camp here over the weekend. So the monastery ceremony is very crowded on Saturdays by the locals. We were the only tourists attending the ceremony. The fotos were taken on Sunday when everybody was on their way back to UB. 
</desc>
    <sym>Campground</sym>
    <type>user</type>
    <extensions>
      <gpxx:WaypointExtension>
        <gpxx:DisplayMode>SymbolAndName</gpxx:DisplayMode>
